    <title>triskelion spiral</title>
    <content type='html'>Maybe inspired by looking at &lt;a href="http://www.mathrecreation.com/2012/10/borges-escher-origami-tessellations.html"&gt;those snake limits or water-bomb twists&lt;/a&gt;, I was looking at spirals again today (see a post &lt;a href="http://www.mathrecreation.com/2011/09/spirals.html"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; from a bout a year ago). This time, looking at spirals that are generated when you take a polygon, rotate it, and grow it several times. Here's one made up of about sixty triangles:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg-pqOO2PN9vypS0fwZPgYcIJHUpmN-9rda1MARFSRw8CbnXxg5j745-hiCpUW4wkRTuJvinZOfVhZg_9ItvlTABeSkCmrtdG1KwW8OiZ0e6d8A8AtvcWQClcV4Ny3ZZT91xQWE3h_oaeg/s1600/backwards_triangle.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" height="395" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg-pqOO2PN9vypS0fwZPgYcIJHUpmN-9rda1MARFSRw8CbnXxg5j745-hiCpUW4wkRTuJvinZOfVhZg_9ItvlTABeSkCmrtdG1KwW8OiZ0e6d8A8AtvcWQClcV4Ny3ZZT91xQWE3h_oaeg/s400/backwards_triangle.JPG" width="400" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This spiral reminded me of the &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isle_of_Man"&gt;Manx&lt;/a&gt; flag - which is a motif that is sometimes called the &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Triskelion"&gt;triskelion&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhboJsocBpcAFPAWgTwukcWEnKafkLRoeijq1ujTXm63hbjMkrbyC6HX24AKz22E3f2BU-FDAtIfaAAk5K0t5ihv2aL5dzsvRjMqQilIR1Yn9EAFaqdqobnnDJ51AYO1dPY9NsPLVE2OTc/s1600/manx.JPG" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" height="182" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhboJsocBpcAFPAWgTwukcWEnKafkLRoeijq1ujTXm63hbjMkrbyC6HX24AKz22E3f2BU-FDAtIfaAAk5K0t5ihv2aL5dzsvRjMqQilIR1Yn9EAFaqdqobnnDJ51AYO1dPY9NsPLVE2OTc/s200/manx.JPG" width="200" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
